<li>劣势<span class="mojikumi-line-end">：</span>花时间<span class="mojikumi-line-end">，</span>费精力<span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span><del><span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span><span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span></del></li>
<li>可随时退出<ins>？</ins></li>
</ul>
